Package org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.alt

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AAConverter
    This class is used to do conversions between different alternating automata, or between alternating automaton and finite automaton.
    AAConverter.CNFABW2NBWConverter  
    AbstractAltAutomaton
    An AbstractAltAutomaton is a structure for automata with alternation which can be in DNF form or CNF form.
    AbstractAltAutomatonCreator
    This is an abstract creator for creating alternating automata with propositional alphabet and labels on transitions.
    AltAutomaton
    An AltAutomaton is an alternating automaton which can be in DNF form or CNF form.
    AltConnector
    An AltConnector has type State but acts as a connector in an alternating automaton.
    AltState
    An AltState is a state of an alternating automaton.
    AltStyleConversion
    This class provides a conversion from an alternating automaton in DNF (or CNF) to an alternating automaton in CNF (or DNF respectively).
    AltTransition
    An AltTransition is a transition in an alternating automaton.
    CNFABWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating Büchi word automaton (ABW) in CNF form.
    CNFACWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating co-Büchi word automaton (ACW) in CNF form.
    CNFAGBWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating generalized Büchi word automaton (AGBW) in CNF form.
    CNFAMWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating Muller word automaton (AMW) in CNF form.
    CNFAPWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating parity word automaton (APW) in CNF form.
    CNFARWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating Rabin word automaton (ARW) in CNF form.
    CNFASWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating Streett word automaton (ASW) in CNF form.
    DNFABW2NBW
    This class implements the conversion from ABW in DNF to equivalent NBW [Satoru Miyano, Takeshi Hayashi: Alternating Finite Automata on ω-Words.
    DNFABWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating Büchi word automaton (ABW) in DNF form.
    DNFACWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating co-Büchi word automaton (ACW) in DNF form.
    DNFAGBWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating generalized Büchi word automaton (AGBW) in DNF form.
    DNFAMWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating Muller word automaton (AMW) in DNF form.
    DNFAPWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating parity word automaton (APW) in DNF form.
    DNFARWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating Rabin word automaton (ARW) in DNF form.
    DNFASWCreator
    This is a creator that can create an alternating Streett word automaton (ASW) in DNF form.
  • Enum Summary
